    "content": "return ( ); \"use client\"; interface PlaybookPageLayoutProps children: ReactNode; : PlaybookPageLayoutProps) return ( /* Content */ children /* Footer */ ); return ( /* Header Block */ Operations Playbook Where Things Live Google Drive File System &amp; Naming Conventions /* Section 1: Folder Structure */ 1 . Folder Structure /* Folder Tree Diagram */ CM Clients 2026 [Client Name] 1-Assets (logo, brand, images) 2-Strategy (proposals, plans) 3-Deliverables (pages, emails, workflows) 4-Client Inputs (from client) 5-Training &amp; Docs (guides, recordings) 6-Admin (contract, invoices) /* What Goes Where Table */ What Goes Where Folder Contents 1-Assets Logo files, brand colors, fonts, photos, headshots 2-Strategy Proposal, strategy doc, funnel map, project scope 3-Deliverables Landing page designs, email copy, workflow screenshots 4-Client Inputs Onboarding form, testimonials, content from client 5-Training &amp; Docs User guides, training recordings, handoff documentation 6-Admin Contract, invoices, payment receipts /* Section 2: File Naming Convention */ 2 . File Naming Convention Format: \" \" YYYY-MM-DD_ClientAbbrev_Description_v# /* Examples Table */ /* Good vs Bad Examples Comparison - Standardized Pattern */ /* Good Examples Card */ Good Examples 2026-01-15_XB_Homepage_v1.pdf 2026-01-20_XB_EmailSequence_v2.docx 2026-02-01_ABC_Proposal_v1.pdf /* Bad Examples Card */ Bad Examples homepage final.pdf email seq FINAL FINAL.docx ABC coaching proposal.pdf /* Version Control Rules */ Version Control Rules v1, v2, v3 — Use version numbers, increment for each revision Never use: &quot;FINAL&quot; , &quot;NEW&quot; , &quot;Updated&quot; , &quot;Copy of&quot; Keep old versions — Don&apos;t delete; latest version is highest number /* Section 3: Access & Sharing Rules */ 3 . Access &amp; Sharing Rules Folder Team Access Client Access 1-Assets Ops, Marketing, Web Dev View only 2-Strategy Ops, Founder View only (approved docs) 3-Deliverables Ops, Marketing, Web Dev Comment (for feedback) 4-Client Inputs Ops Edit (upload access) 5-Training &amp; Docs Ops, Web Dev View only 6-Admin Founder, Finance only No access /* New Client Folder Setup Checklist */ New Client Folder Setup Checklist Create folder: CM Clients &gt; 2026 &gt; [Client Name] Create all 6 subfolders (copy template structure) Set sharing permissions per matrix above Share 4-Client Inputs folder link with client /* Footer */ Owner: Operations Coordinator ); google drive files folders naming convention storage organization where things live file structure client folder assets deliverables version control sharing access permissions doc naming versioning"
